3.20	Afraid_of_Sunlight	Afraid of Sunlight	Afraid of Sunlight is Marillion's eighth studio album, released in 1995. It was their last for EMI (who would, however, continue to release back-catalogue material on compilations and re-issues, as well as distribute some later recordings).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/73/Afraid-of-sunlight.jpeg/220px-Afraid-of-sunlight.jpeg
